# The first handwritten note (automatically added to the journal)
Day 1. Beach. I don't remember the name.\
I woke up in the middle of nowhere, on this rotten ship. My head hurts.\
There is a strange sandwich and this log in my pockets.\
Someone has already written in the journal. The handwriting looks like mine... but I'm not sure.\
[n+]\
Admiral? Dock Alpha? Tells me nothing.\
I'll sail somewhere. Maybe I'll remember.